WEBVTT

00:09.558 --> 00:11.599
To your knowledge, did
the Departed drink more

00:11.600 --> 00:12.974
than two alcoholic
beverages daily?

00:12.975 --> 00:15.475
Yes.

00:18.141 --> 00:20.182
To your knowledge,
was the Departed

00:20.183 --> 00:22.140
born in a hospital?

00:22.141 --> 00:24.058
I think so.

00:25.558 --> 00:29.558
To your knowledge,
did the Departed ever
attempt suicide?

00:36.433 --> 00:38.558
I don't know.

00:41.600 --> 00:45.640
I understand you want
to protect your
husband's privacy,

00:45.641 --> 00:47.974
but the more questions
you answer honestly,

00:47.975 --> 00:50.933
the better chance
your claim will be
processed.

00:54.433 --> 00:57.057
He told me...

00:59.058 --> 01:01.432
He took some pills once

01:01.433 --> 01:03.558
in high school.

01:08.433 --> 01:10.933
So is that a "yes"?

01:15.391 --> 01:16.932
Yes.

