advantage of these
poor, grieving people.

27:02.933 --> 27:06.224
But no, no, no, no.
They're coming to us,
you know?

27:06.225 --> 27:08.640
And......
look at this.

27:08.641 --> 27:12.140
140 million bodies disappeared.

27:12.141 --> 27:13.682
