29:30.725 --> 29:33.724
The mirror in the bar?
I wasn't in the bar.

29:33.725 --> 29:36.307
Let's go, Ms. Durst.
Wait! Stop!

29:36.308 --> 29:39.890
You... listen to me!
I wasn't in the bar
last night.

29:39.891 --> 29:43.307
Someone took my badge.
They're... they're
pretending to be me.

29:43.308 --> 29:46.682
See? The conference,
they gave me this

29:46.683 --> 29:48.724
because my badge was stolen.

29:48.725 --> 29:50.432
That's the person
you should be
looking for.

29:50.433 --> 29:52.057
